Installing TressetteNetwork4
========================================
Once the game has been installed, the launcher (available on all systems) will
provide a graphical interface to start a gaming session.

Installing on Linux
========================================
python setup.py build
(then su to root or use sudo)
python setup.py install

Start from terminal:
ts4launcher
- or -
tressettenetwork4 standalone
 for a standalone server.

Installing on Mac OS X
========================================
Same as Linux, but for starting the game you can also use the application icon
you can find in the Application folder.

Installing on Windows
========================================
- use the installer -

You can find the launcher in the Start Menu.
